  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate the Most Disadvantaged Children in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">EMDC will provide up to &#xA3;38.5m (2021-2029) to support 360,000 marginalised children, including 216,000 girls, to gain foundational skills, i.e. literacy, numeracy, socio-emotional and life skills.  EMDC will focus on the poorest girls and children with disabilities, with the goal of improving system-wide support for all marginalised children.</narrative>
  </description>
